                        <h5 class="mb-0 mt-1">Ability to add music videos to favorites</h5>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <section class="py-4 py-xl-5">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="text-center p-4 p-lg-5">
                    <h1 class="fw-bold mb-4"><br>How important is music in our lives?</h1>
                    <p><br>Music makes us better, inspires, gives unforgettable feelings. It is thanks to music
                        that a person is able to relax, get some food for the mind. This kind of art can radically change a
                        person's mood – cheer him up, sadden him, feel longing.&nbsp;<br><br></p>
                    <p class="text-warning">See how many views a random music video from Youtube has to make sure of this.<br></p>
                    <div class="YoUvideo" style="text-align: center">
                        <iframe width="1000" height="700" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/<%= video_Id%>" title="YouTube video player"
                                frameBorder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                                allowFullScreen></iframe>
                    </div>
